# Per-contributor Claude Code state is NOT tracked (e.g. settings.local.json),
# EXCEPT the shared project skills under .claude/skills/, which are committed so
# teammates and CI get them. ".claude/*" ignores the directory's contents but
# not the directory itself, so "!.claude/skills/" can re-include just the skills.
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
.codex/
.cursor/
.aider*
# Rendered APISIX route file. Tracked source of truth is
# api-gateway/apisix.yaml.template; scripts/render-apisix-config.sh
# produces this file with real secrets substituted from the host env.
api-gateway/apisix.yaml.local

# Build-phase agent scaffolding (process docs, GOAL packets, resume state) — local only.
/.agents/
